# Credentials are no longer read from .env at runtime.
#
# Enter each provider's username/email and password in the app: click the gear
# icon next to the Source / Destination provider dropdowns. Credentials are
# stored encrypted (keychain-backed) in the app-data directory.
#
# For a one-time migration off an old .env, you may temporarily set the values
# below (uppercase names) and launch the app once; they will be imported into
# the encrypted store, after which this file can be deleted.
#
# ZOOPLA_SOURCE_USERNAME=""
# ZOOPLA_SOURCE_PASSWORD=""
# ZOOPLA_DESTINATION_USERNAME=""
# ZOOPLA_DESTINATION_PASSWORD=""
